text.tspan: SUNDIAL turns on Do-Not-Disturb for you. Using the
pomodoro technique, your tasks get organized into
short 'sprints' to keep your full attention.
It's easy to fill up your tasks, with a built-in list tool and
popular calendar integrations. Simplify and categorize
your workload with the auto-tagging feature.
Breaks are automatically shuffled into your list of tasks,
and the app provides suggestions for exercise, drinking
water, or other activities to stay fit & healthy.
